+/*
+ * Driver for LynLoong PC extras
+ *
+ *  Copyright (C) 2009 Lemote Inc.
+ *  Author: Wu Zhangjin <wuzhangjin@gmail.com>, Xiang Yu <xiangy@lemote.com>
+ *
